@startuml
autonumber

<style>
sequenceDiagram {
    box {
        Padding 10
    }
    participant {
        Padding 10
    }
}
</style>

actor "Aluno (Autenticado)" as Aluno
box "Front-End (React)" #LightBlue
    participant "VantagensPage" as View
    participant "AuthContext" as Auth
    participant "api.ts (Axios)" as API
end box

box "Back-End (Spring Boot)" #LightCyan
    participant "VantagemController" as Ctrl
    participant "VantagemRepository" as VantRepo
    participant "CupomRepository" as CupomRepo
end box

database "Banco de Dados" as DB #LightGray

title UC07 - Visualizar Vantagens e Cupons Resgatados

== Inicialização da Página (Carregamento) ==

Aluno -> View : 1. Acessa a Loja/Painel de Vantagens
activate View

View -> Auth : 2. Recupera dados da sessão (usuario.id)
activate Auth
Auth --> View : 3. Retorna usuario.id e saldoAtual
deactivate Auth

View -> API : 4. listarTodasVantagens() e listarMeusCupons(usuario.id)
activate API

API -> Ctrl : 5. GET /api/vantagens (Listar Ativas)
activate Ctrl
Ctrl -> VantRepo : findByAtivaTrue()
activate VantRepo
VantRepo -> DB : SELECT * FROM vantagem WHERE ativa = true
activate DB
DB --> VantRepo : Lista de Vantagens
deactivate DB
VantRepo --> Ctrl : List<Vantagem>
deactivate VantRepo
Ctrl --> API : 200 OK (List<VantagemResponse>)

API -> Ctrl : 6. GET /api/cupons/aluno/{alunoId}
Ctrl -> CupomRepo : findByAlunoId(alunoId)
activate CupomRepo
CupomRepo -> DB : SELECT * FROM cupom WHERE aluno_id = ?
activate DB
DB --> CupomRepo : Lista de Cupons (Código, Data, Empresa)
deactivate DB
CupomRepo --> Ctrl : List<Cupom>
deactivate CupomRepo
Ctrl --> API : 200 OK (List<CupomResponse>)
deactivate Ctrl

API --> View : 7. Retorna dados combinados (Vantagens e Cupons)
deactivate API

View -> View : setVantagens(data.vantagens)\nsetMeusCupons(data.cupons)
note over View #LightYellow : Renderiza os cards de vantagens\ne a tabela com os códigos de cupons já gerados

View --> Aluno : 8. Exibe a tela montada com saldo e listagens atualizadas
deactivate View

@enduml